rc=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:24:35.000Z","msg":"幫推比文宣thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[文宣marketing]不如將「香港人日程表」個名upgrade下？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0906f86aee5a464bfcc82c9d24881da924e664e","tid":1390674,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"ae7a53e133bc26a531d604da31961bbc24d979e2","tid":1390674,"uid":293426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"怒推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港反擊戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb103f580ffdde25e4a68c8faf0e18e44a2fd57","tid":1390674,"uid":266937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e008bb12798a8585220e318729561c3e3f0f8617","tid":1390674,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5965c044357a7b4726ca14823207d9363777002a","tid":1390674,"uid":159002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54b12c2e5d74f61daa6edb7fa54ab2868c9ad9ec","tid":1390674,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:05:16.000Z","msg":"加油！ 下次同香港人傾遏前試下講以下嘅句子做開場白<br />\n<br />\n1.黑警死全家<br />\n2.光復香港 時代革命<br />\n3.林鄭下台<br />\n4.我要真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n效果可能好啲！加油！"},{"pid":"3f9c616259ad44f192217f495541c34b8fd752e6","tid":1390674,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:05:40.000Z","msg":"加油！ 下次同香港人傾遏前試下講以下嘅句子做開場白<br />\n<br />\n1.黑警死全家<br />\n2.光復香港 時代革命<br />\n3.林鄭下台<br />\n4.我要真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n效果可能好啲！加油！"},{"pid":"bee95be0599818205a38bb0127f5415cbe34e06d","tid":1390674,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7f9c548f5f17197af5f62a424c1eb0975f8a5a","tid":1390674,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年內落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年內！"},{"pid":"593e0d1ed9f1d94fc25fee4a88026e3731bb2a76","tid":1390674,"uid":279895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e26f661f44119344468de9cebc2ab2a7e53d6e74","tid":1390674,"uid":200855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040ca0da3ce98f4af941f62ec97b2ea55424793f","tid":1390674,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"唔止要推，幫手宣傳開去"},{"pid":"eb77aa46c94ab7ed559448c02fea516f7f5a41a5","tid":1390674,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:05:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f31756101694b30254ee76ec1396627a6f5de249","tid":1390674,"uid":13143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:25:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f8112e6a24a53778077898c1c7dae43493e0970","tid":1390674,"uid":37529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"552801eb3fd5bad8669e9151f0150cd4a2b08cd5","tid":1390674,"uid":173429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a1fb1c61c716b74df81bde930a74814c3a5f778","tid":1390674,"uid":202889,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kuxd6ij.png\" data-t